name: Dark Rabbit
description:
The other day I went to the natural science museum to practice my drawing. It was pretty empty due to the pandemic so I had the whole place to myself. Everything was normal until I walked into the taxidermy room, I don't know if it was the stories I made up in my head or the heavy silence in the room, but suddenly the lights turned off and I can swear... that something moved in there.

Part of the "Luz Mala" collection
